{"tid":1826653,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"★中國製 UOS 20 正式版發佈　介面率先看","createTime":"2020-01-16T10:02:35.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-17T08:50:15.000Z","uid":19454,"like":1,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"376c7a46b8afdb224a471a37c539d9d914a5fdc3","tid":1826653,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-16T10:02:35.000Z","msg":"日前，有消息指中國打算在 3 年內將外國的電腦裝置及軟件由外國貨換成中國貨。電腦方面，相信沒有人會質疑中國品牌電腦能夠取代外國品牌（如 hp、Dell、Apple），不過軟件方面特别是 Microsoft Windows 又有沒有取代方案呢？忽然，一套名為 UOS 的作業系統出現。今天，UOS 正式向合作伙伴發佈 UOS 20 正式版，讓我們一窺這套中國製 OS 真面目。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.newmobilelife.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/01/7566d40e698e5d8c6c45660e28edabb4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.newmobilelife.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F01%2F7566d40e698e5d8c6c45660e28edabb4.jpg&h=18ffc6f2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n操作介面跟 Windows 相約<br />\nUOS 其實是一套基於 Debian 10.x 而開發的作業系統，就像 Redhat 的 Gnome、Suse 的 KDE、Ubuntu 的 Unity 一般。UOS 的桌面佈局跟 Windows 分别不太大，左下方是操作選單，下方有任務欄，打開應用程式後，右方有像 Windows 的放大、縮小、關閉按鈕。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.newmobilelife.com/2020/01/16/uos20-release/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.newmobilelife.com%2F2020%2F01%2F16%2Fuos20-release%2F&d=LzGu2J%2BtBqWvyoHzd7Q7GJhbjDs%2B%2F0Yai8vOOt2IPjE%3D&h=464b2ecc\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.newmobilelife.com/2020/01/16/uos20-release/</a>"},{"pid":"5f83fe8e2775df01f0154d64461b71046c01f7bc","tid":1826653,"uid":19454,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-16T10:03:17.000Z","msg":"自家 &ldquo;App Store&rdquo;<br />\n跟其他 Linux 一般，UOS 也有自家的 &ldquo;App Store&rdquo; 應用商店，按軟件類别區分，例如網絡應用類可找到 Firefox、百度網盤、360 安全瀏覽器、迅雷等 Windows 常用軟件。<br />\n<br />\n通過 UOS 公司的認證系統，日後更可讓其他軟件開發者在此平台發售軟件。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.newmobilelife.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/01/uos3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.newmobilelife.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F01%2Fuos3.jpg&h=bd335d11&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n支援不同平台<br />\nUOS 可支持 x86、龍芯、申威、ARM 等國產 CPU 平台，能夠替代微軟 Windows 操作系統，滿足不同用戶的辦公、生活、娛樂需求。"},{"pid":"4310034cde4aab325b045347f0a0577eb354cf23","tid":1826653,"uid":53062,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-16T10:03:28.000Z","msg":"咁似linux"},{"pid":"5148a78e2e664138c864dbcfe1d37cfc4e437977","tid":1826653,"uid":205339,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-16T10:03:39.000Z","msg":"John linux"},{"pid":"8b27558a17b754a68df0282ca4f2e6cff4eac51c","tid":1826653,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-16T10:03:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.newmobilelife.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/01/uos2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.newmobilelife.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F01%2Fuos2.jpg&h=71995d8f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"2fc6b20df8422cf9d10580a93e6b9cbbcdaa8bf8","tid":1826653,"uid":19454,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-16T10:04:42.000Z","msg":"just copy"},{"pid":"288feb22ffff907e24cb3afb99a171e068f3787a","tid":1826653,"uid":166462,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-16T10:05:39.000Z","msg":"又羊"},{"pid":"69ca88d4bea7f01f5207ea71f4c75b1eba61e411","tid":1826653,"uid":245849,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"quote":{"pid":"4310034cde4aab325b045347f0a0577eb354cf23","tid":1826653,"uid":53062,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-16T10:03:28.000Z","msg":"咁似linux"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-16T10:11:54.000Z","msg":"就係linux嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n改個UI加個App Store咁大把<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n而且睇怕可能連個UI都係偷<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":